# add the nav widget to all pages
@widget navigation 4 1 12 to welcome-page to version-page to scenario-page to pc-knowledge-page;
@widget navigation 4 1 12 to welcome-page to linux-knowledge-page to installation-page to old-hardware-page to help-page;
